{"tid":1838712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔理你罷工又好，驚死又好全香港都一定撐","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T08:05:20.000Z","uid":4064,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f25f581bd8532f310ddb95ceab0e60e650dc8ab9","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"各位醫護手足，錫住自己條命<br />\n<br />\n信政府唔帶口罩班撚樣由佢地自然淘汰<br />\n<br />\n真香港人一定識帶口罩洗手果堆基本野<br />\n<br />\n唔好為左班大陸喱同堆返大陸既藍絲冇左條命<br />\n<br />\n總之你地罷工迫港共封關又好，真驚死唔返工又好，攰得滯去旅行散心又好<br />\n<br />\n全香港人都一撚定撐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家係早期階段大部分都係外來case<br />\n<br />\n比較少香港本土case要處理<br />\n<br />\n罷工放假對真正香港人黎講仲係最低影響階段<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留住條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0372727857676d9d4b94d7774063994b8c987f","tid":1838712,"uid":285899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"推 呢個政府不值香港人去犧牲"},{"pid":"1c4981de5c9ab0b95150539ceed5520e6d9e9495","tid":1838712,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5b5fcb29cff0d6d0fa16258479a92113c9635f7","tid":1838712,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31770324d8b5c5a9351033474fcef4751aca44d1","tid":1838712,"uid":269119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"0afcbbe0641353e28f36d275e2cd302347d0762e","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"記住而家中招既係咩人點解中招<br />\n<br />\n你就知自己條命對重光既香港幾重要<br />\n<br />\n如果你因為呢一刻既做使命感而有咩冬瓜豆腐<br />\n<br />\n你就唔能夠保護重光後既香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地既專業知識同經驗對重光後既香港係至關重要<br />\n<br />\n唔好送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e662675a2c2a1dd80ad7ca2388e4f53c6807a73c","tid":1838712,"uid":61197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦罷啦"},{"pid":"03e999bb17d4e2bf1fa67db189ca1bff707a9623","tid":1838712,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d721b19e679080c1cc7172325dbf5a5a6302400","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"我知道你地有一種感覺係你地一定要企出黎做應該做既事<br />\n<br />\n我身邊個個醫護FD都有<br />\n<br />\n但係你要認清楚咩叫應該做既事<br />\n救香港人先係應該做既野<br />\n<br />\n救大陸人/白痴信政府返大陸既人唔係香港人<br />\n<br />\n如果你因為呢班垃圾而有事,你就救唔到需要你救既香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果班垃圾真係由佢自然淘汰啦好麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d31961a6cb90454e78e338560d12f47bedbe2a1","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"如果仲有醫護手足係好爭扎既<br />\n<br />\n睇一次呢個POST入面既留言:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1632589490222457/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F156468627834558%2Fposts%2F1632589490222457%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=ff3c6a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1632589490222457/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n你要救既,就係呢堆人<br />\n如果你已經視死如歸既<br />\n諗下你死既原因係因為呢堆人<br />\n你甘心嗎?<br />\n<br />\n唔甘心既就罷工放假去旅行啦好麻<br />\n最多最多等呢班低智動物死左一堆喇<br />\n<br />\n開始真係有真香港人中招先返黎幫拖呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec34340aafdf430e459a42f912f5f19be43c2cb","tid":1838712,"uid":296491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"得佢地罷唔夠，我地要一齊行<br />\n<br />\n唔只醫護，應該全港大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與醫護同行，全港大三罷！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b4385addae469f22aa08dbb4b75b4195959ab38","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c20ad1d7eb7694b6435116e7c1ac7d6894c07dc","tid":1838712,"uid":21920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:52:09.000Z","msg":"一定支持醫護人員<br />\n垃圾港共防疫冇做好<br />\n依家就要D醫護抽生死簽送死<br />\n支持罷工交返個波比港共"},{"pid":"5368e37efd06b43ad3a7c849d760639d16343f40","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c20ad1d7eb7694b6435116e7c1ac7d6894c07dc","tid":1838712,"uid":21920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:52:09.000Z","msg":"一定支持醫護人員<br />\n垃圾港共防疫冇做好<br />\n依家就要D醫護抽生死簽送死<br />\n支持罷工交返個波比港共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"重點係而家中招果班係蝗蟲黎<br />\n憑咩要香港人拎自己條命出黎醫?"},{"pid":"7d892b8a6a1b0631849ceabbd4d9d7c5d3cff3fd","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d48fbeec19bab0e5bc3a1b35ba3319f7e7a8f6","tid":1838712,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":